# Bindings
bind-key j down
bind-key k up
bind-key j next articlelist
bind-key k prev articlelist
bind-key J next-feed articlelist
bind-key K prev-feed articlelist
bind-key g home

# Macros
browser qutebrowser
macro , open-in-browser
macro v set browser "i3 exec mpv"; open-in-browser ; set browser qutebrowser
macro p set browser "lynx" open-in-browser ; set browser qutebrowser

# Colors
